<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1><i class="fas fa-headset"></i> TIMEON KAIROS Support</h1>

    <div class="faq" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
      <h3><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Response Time</h3>
      <p>We respond within 2 working days (Monâ€“Fri). For urgent issues, add "URGENT" to your subject.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
      <h3><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> What We Support</h3>
      <p>We handle password, access keys, payment, registration, results, and other portal issues. Kindly allow 2 working days for a reply.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-form" id="formSection">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Contact Us</h2>
      <form id="supportForm">
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Type your message or complaint here..." required></textarea>
        <button type="submit" id="sendBtn"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i> Send Message</button>
        <div id="contactTimer">You can send a message to us below.</div>
        <div id="cooldownTimer"></div>
        <div id="notification"></div>
        <div class="loader" id="loader"><i class="fas fa-spinner"></i> Sending...</div>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="success-message" id="successMessage">
      <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i><br><br>
      Your message was sent successfully! We will get back to you shortly.
